{
  "manifest_version": 2,
  "name": "vllm-full",
  "runner": "docker-compose",
  "docker_compose_file": "{\"services\":{\"vllm-proxy\":{\"image\":\"nearaidev/vllm-proxy@sha256:e641e65c919d92434446f801dfd0fc92a8524d25c7594f2faef9cf2732ae4dc6\",\"container_name\":\"vllm-proxy\",\"ports\":[\"8000:8000\"],\"privileged\":true,\"user\":\"root\",\"volumes\":[\"/var/run/dstack.sock:/var/run/dstack.sock\"],\"environment\":[\"MODEL_NAME=Qwen/Qwen2.5-0.5B-Instruct\",\"TOKEN=dcml-test-token\",\"VLLM_BASE_URL=http://vllm:8000\",\"DEV=1\",\"NVIDIA_VISIBLE_DEVICES=all\"],\"deploy\":{\"resources\":{\"reservations\":{\"devices\":[{\"driver\":\"nvidia\",\"count\":1,\"capabilities\":[\"gpu\"]}]}}},\"depends_on\":{\"vllm\":{\"condition\":\"service_healthy\"}},\"restart\":\"unless-stopped\"},\"vllm\":{\"image\":\"vllm/vllm-openai@sha256:e72c6a4d3b690f48d6f1ba08ad8ed2310848e36e28c30c19e21c283d87354d72\",\"container_name\":\"vllm\",\"ipc\":\"host\",\"privileged\":true,\"ulimits\":{\"memlock\":-1,\"nofile\":{\"soft\":65535,\"hard\":65535}},\"volumes\":[\"huggingface_cache:/root/.cache/huggingface\",\"vllm_cache:/root/.cache/vllm\"],\"environment\":[\"VLLM_LOGGING_LEVEL=INFO\",\"NVIDIA_VISIBLE_DEVICES=all\",\"NVIDIA_DRIVER_CAPABILITIES=compute,utility\",\"VLLM_CACHE_ROOT=/root/.cache/vllm\"],\"command\":\"Qwen/Qwen2.5-0.5B-Instruct --gpu-memory-utilization 0.9 --max-model-len 4096 --max-num-seqs 32\\n\",\"deploy\":{\"resources\":{\"reservations\":{\"devices\":[{\"driver\":\"nvidia\",\"count\":1,\"capabilities\":[\"gpu\"]}]}}},\"healthcheck\":{\"test\":[\"CMD\",\"curl\",\"-f\",\"http://localhost:8000/v1/models\"],\"interval\":\"30s\",\"timeout\":\"10s\",\"retries\":60,\"start_period\":\"300s\"},\"restart\":\"unless-stopped\"}},\"volumes\":{\"huggingface_cache\":null,\"vllm_cache\":null}}",
  "kms_enabled": false,
  "gateway_enabled": false,
  "local_key_provider_enabled": false,
  "key_provider": "none",
  "public_logs": true,
  "public_sysinfo": true,
  "public_tcbinfo": true
}
